5
00:01:38,310 --> 00:01:41,290
Recently, I composed a new song.

6
00:01:42,390 --> 00:01:45,770
"A Lonely Man."

7
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:51,110
Little Sister Damai, want to listen to it?

8
00:01:57,110 --> 00:01:58,850
I'd love to.

9
00:01:58,850 --> 00:02:01,490
Okay, I'll sing it for you.

10
