31
00:03:55,560 --> 00:04:00,100
♪ <i>You've never forgotten</i> ♪

32
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:05,560
♪ <i>I hope you can forgive my past foolishness</i> ♪

33
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:09,820
♪ <i>Be fine</i> ♪

34
00:04:09,820 --> 00:04:13,080
♪ <i>It'll be fine</i> ♪

