- Yeah.

259
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:02,900
You look so sprightly.

260
00:17:02,900 --> 00:17:04,200
Of course, Granny.

261
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,700
I'm even more dashing now.

262
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:09,400
Granny, what's that? It smells amazing.

263
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:12,500
You'll love it. They're all your favorites.

264
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,700
Wash your hands first.

265
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:15,000
Got it, I'll wash my hands.

266
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:17,000
You say the same thing every time.

267
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:19,200
